messages.message: Hi team, I clicked on a link to a ground truth set for an app. It seems I'm able to see data about it even without logging in (link (https://aihub-uat.internal.instabase.com/hub/apps/819ec38e-ce11-4dfa-b6b4-529ede3815af/ground-truths/472)). I think we should look into hiding the data if the user is not logged in

this is a public app, so that's why you're able to view these app details without logging in

this is expected behavior!
